  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oil in a deep frying pan to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Thread one padron pepper onto each bamboo skewer.",
    "In a bowl, mix together garlic, lemon juice, salt, black pepper, and paprika.",
    "Brush the garlic mixture onto both sides of the padron peppers.",
    "Fry the padron pepper skewers in batches until they are golden brown and crispy.",
    "Remove the skewers from the oil with a slotted spoon and place them on a paper towel-lined plate.",
    "Serve the fragrant fried Syrian padron peppers skewers hot.",
    "Garnish with additional paprika and lemon wedges if desired."
  ],
